WEBVTT

00:00.605 --> 00:01.955
<i>Previously on "Switched at Birth"...</i>

00:03.774 --> 00:05.017
What's going on?

00:05.018 --> 00:07.759
_

00:09.713 --> 00:11.314
Don't follow me.

00:11.348 --> 00:12.481
I can hook you guys up with some coke.

00:12.516 --> 00:14.350
- Have you done this before?
- No, no, no,

00:14.384 --> 00:17.119
but this is good. This is really good.

00:17.154 --> 00:20.022
Daphne, I'm trying to get
through this, just like you.

00:20.057 --> 00:22.058
You really want to know how my trip was?

00:22.092 --> 00:23.125
Yeah.

00:23.160 --> 00:25.194
I got very high.

00:25.229 --> 00:27.863
You know what? You are not the
only one going through stuff,

00:27.898 --> 00:29.865
so stop acting like a little brat.

00:31.935 --> 00:33.169
Look, if you're really pissed at your ma,

00:33.203 --> 00:34.904
and you need her to know,
then you gotta show her.

00:38.075 --> 00:41.010
I can't believe I just
did that. I'm on probation.

00:41.044 --> 00:42.044
A bad girl, huh?

00:50.687 --> 00:51.921
I'm just really worried about her.

